'''北京英国学校'''（'''British School of Beijing'''）是一所位于[[北京|北京]]的英国国际学校，创立于2003年。<ref>"[https://www.cobis.org.uk/uploaded/COBIS_-_Our_Schools/BSO_Inspection_Reports/The_British_School_of_Beijing_BSO_Report.pdf INSPECTION REPORT ON THE BRITISH SCHOOL OF BEIJING, SHUNYI] {{Wayback|url=https://www.cobis.org.uk/uploaded/COBIS_-_Our_Schools/BSO_Inspection_Reports/The_British_School_of_Beijing_BSO_Report.pdf |date=20151003055522 }}" (). {{link-en|Council of British International Schools|Council of British International Schools}} (COBIS) Independent Schools Inspectorate. p. 1 (PDF p. 6/19). Retrieved on October 2, 2015.</ref> 在北京，{{link-en|Nord Anglia Education|Nord Anglia Education}}有两个英国国际学校：BSB[[顺义|顺义]]校区和BSB[[三里屯|三里屯]]校区。

2013年BSB是第二大北京的国际学校。<ref name=Stefonek>Stefonek, Jonathan. "[http://europe.chinadaily.com.cn/life/2012-10/07/content_15798976.htm Passion for teaching English-style grows in Beijing suburbs] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6bxePTLhH?url=http://web.archive.org/web/20151001194200/http://europe.chinadaily.com.cn/life/2012-10/07/content_15798976.htm |date=20151001194329 |dateformat=iso }}" (). ''[[China_Daily|China Daily]]''. 7 October 2012. Retrieved on 2 October 2015. "The British School addressed that particular need, he says, and then grew quite quickly to become the second largest international school in Beijing. "</ref> 

2011年BSB[[校长|校长]]Mike Embley表示，BSB是北京侨民社群的中心。<ref name=Mansell>Mansell, Warwick. "[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/expateducation/8473432/Expat-guide-to-China-schools.html Expat guide to China: schools] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6bvzSvb0U?url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/expateducation/8473432/Expat-guide-to-China-schools.html |date=20150930173138 |dateformat=iso }}" (). ''[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Telegraph]]''. 27 April 2011. Retrieved on October 1, 2015. "The British School of Beijing is said by its head to be the hub of its expat community, attracting parents from British and other embassies as well as those working for major multi-nationals."</ref>

